]] and [[Jennifer Aniston]] |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2011|2|8}} |DirectedBy=B.J. Porter |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=13 |Title=Will Ferrell and Jon Hamm |Aux1=[[Will Ferrell]] and [[Jon Hamm]] |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2011|5|22}} |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=14 |Title=Oscar Buzz Edition Part 1 |Aux1=[[Jennifer Lawrence]], [[Naomi Watts]], [[Christoph Waltz]], [[Anne Hathaway]] and [[Amy Adams]] |DirectedBy=Ruben Fleischer |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|2|11}} |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=15 |Title=Oscar Buzz Edition Part 2 |Aux1=[[Jessica Chastain]], [[Sally Field]], [[Emmanuel Lewis]], and [[Bradley Cooper]] |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|2|12}} |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=16 |Title=James Franco |Aux1=[[James Franco]], [[Edward Norton]], and [[The Lonely Island]] |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|5|7}} |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=17 |Title=Justin Bieber |Aux1=[[Justin Bieber]] |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|9|26}} |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=N/A |Title=Happy Holidays Edition |Aux1=[[Tobey Maguire]], [[Samuel L. Jackson]], and [[Arcade Fire]] |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2013|12|18}} |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=18 |Title=President Barack Obama |Aux1=[[President of the United States|President]] [[Barack Obama]] |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2014|3|11}} |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=19 |Title=Brad Pitt |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2014|10|22}} |Aux1=[[Brad Pitt]] and [[Louis C.K.]] |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode list |EpisodeNumber=20 |Title=Hillary Clinton |OriginalAirDate={{Start date|2016|9|22}} |Aux1=[[Hillary Clinton]] |DirectedBy=Scott Aukerman |LineColor=9cc0ff }} {{Episode l